OL,3,CRoyal Mail misses annual delivery
OL,4,Ctargets for another year running
OL,6,FRoyal Mail has missed its delivery
OL,7,Ftargets for another year, but said
OL,8,Fmore first-class mail has been sent on
OL,9,Ftime over recent weeks.
OL,11,FThis is after the postal service
OL,12,Fpledged to invest #500 million in
OL,13,Fimproving its service.
OL,15,FAround 75.7% of first-class mail
OL,16,Farrived the next working day over the
OL,17,F12 months to the end of March,
OL,18,Faccording to the latest quality of
OL,19,Fservice report.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
