CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780128432
OL,3,CRoyal Mail misses annual delivery
OL,4,Ctargets for another year running
OL,6,FThis was slightly less than the 76.3%
OL,7,Fachieved in the prior year.
OL,9,FFor second-class mail, 90.2% was
OL,10,Fdelivered within three working days `
OL,11,Fless than the 92.2% achieved the year
OL,12,Fbefore.
OL,14,FThis means that Royal Mail missed
OL,15,Fdelivery targets set by regulator
OL,16,FOfcom for another year running.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
