OL,3,CRoyal Mail misses annual delivery
OL,4,Ctargets for another year running
OL,6,FUnder the watchdog's targets, 90% of
OL,7,Ffirst-class mail should be delivered
OL,8,Fthe next day, and 95% of second-class
OL,9,Fmail should be delivered within three
OL,10,Fdays.
OL,12,FRoyal Mail said it had been a
OL,13,Fchallenging start to the year, and
OL,14,Fthat storms Goretti and Chandra, as
OL,15,Fwell as more staff off sick from the
OL,16,Fflu, had affected its performance over
OL,17,Fthe winter.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
