OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780128432
OL,3,CRoyal Mail misses annual delivery
OL,4,Ctargets for another year running
OL,6,FThe company was fined #21 million by
OL,7,FOfcom in October last year for missing
OL,8,Fits annual targets ` the third-largest
OL,9,Ffine ever imposed by the
OL,10,Fcommunications watchdog.
OL,12,FOfcom said at the time that it was
OL,13,F"unacceptable" that millions of
OL,14,Fimportant letters were arriving late.
OL,16,FDespite performance weakening in the
OL,17,Fpast year, Royal Mail has pointed to
OL,18,Fsigns of improvement within its
OL,19,Fservice over more recent weeks since
OL,20,Fthe end of the last reporting period.
OL,26,@uD@AOUuD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
