OL,3,CRoyal Mail misses annual delivery
OL,4,Ctargets for another year running
OL,6,FIt has consistently been delivering
OL,7,Fmore than 80% of first-class mail on
OL,8,Ftime over April and May, according to
OL,9,Fthe business, following an improved
OL,10,Fperformance at the start of the year.
OL,12,FIt comes as Royal Mail has pledged to
OL,13,Fmeet new delivery targets by May next
OL,14,Fyear as part of a plan to invest #500
OL,15,Fmillion in the service over the next
OL,16,Ffive years.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
