OL,3,CRoyal Mail misses annual delivery
OL,4,Ctargets for another year running
OL,6,FIt has begun to phase in a new letter
OL,7,Fdelivery model nationwide, subject to
OL,8,Fa consultation with union members,
OL,9,Fwhich will see it scrap second-class
OL,10,Fpost on Saturdays.
OL,12,FThe reforms also involve delivering
OL,13,Fsecond-class post every other weekday
OL,14,Fonly.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
