OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780128432
OL,3,CRoyal Mail misses annual delivery
OL,4,Ctargets for another year running
OL,6,FRoyal Mail said the changes and
OL,7,Fplanned investment will lead to it
OL,8,Fimproving first-class next-day
OL,9,Fdelivery to around 85% within nine
OL,10,Fmonths of the reforms being brought
OL,11,Fin, before reaching the 90% target set
OL,12,Fby regulator Ofcom within a year.
OL,14,FThe firm also vowed to deliver 93% of
OL,15,Fsecond-class letters in three days
OL,16,Fwithin the space of nine months, and
OL,17,Fhit the 95% target by May next year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
