OL,3,CRoyal Mail misses annual delivery
OL,4,Ctargets for another year running
OL,6,FThe results of a ballot put to members
OL,7,Fof the Communication Workers Union
OL,8,F(CWU) over the agreed plan is due to
OL,9,Fbe released on Friday.
OL,11,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
