OL,3,CRoyal Mail misses annual delivery
OL,4,Ctargets for another year running
OL,6,FJamie Stephenson, Royal Mail's chief
OL,7,Foperating officer, said: "We're
OL,8,Fputting significant investment into
OL,9,Fimproving reliability and reaching
OL,10,Fthese new delivery targets, but
OL,11,Fdelivering lasting change across a
OL,12,Fnetwork of this scale takes time.
OL,14,F"We have a plan to deploy the new
OL,15,Fdelivery model to all delivery offices
OL,16,Facross the country by the Christmas
OL,17,Fpeak period and have set clear targets
OL,18,Ffor each quarter as changes are
OL,19,Fintroduced across the network.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
